1. About configuration:
	Put confs for env like: nginx, uwsgi or db to ./env-conf

2. About deployment:
    ./deploy.sh to deploy codes & start server, if you want to test locally first:
    1) Change local /etc/hosts and add the line like: 127.0.0.1	realrecorder.net
	2) Open your browser to visit http://realrecorder.net to verify the results.
	3) After deployment on production, open your browser to visit http://www.realrecorder.net to verify the resutls.
	NOTICE: You may need to test firefox, IE, Chrome browsers

3. For any new sites or updates on sites:
    1) Go to google analytics to add goole's javascript.
	2) Go to google webmaster to ask for new review.

